gBots.ai) operates on a strict no-refund policy for all services rendered. Once a service has been delivered or a project has commenced, no refunds will be issued.",{"type":40,"tag":52,"props":64,"children":66},{"id":65},"_2-rationale",[67],{"type":45,"value":68},"2. Rationale",{"type":40,"tag":47,"props":70,"children":71},{},[72],{"type":45,"value":73},"Our no-refund policy is based on the nature of our services:",{"type":40,"tag":47,"props":75,"children":76},{},[77],{"type":45,"value":78},"2.1. Custom Development: Our AI applications, web development, SEO, and digital marketing services are custom-tailored to each client's specific needs. Once work has begun, significant time, resources, and expertise have been invested.",{"type":40,"tag":47,"props":80,"children":81},{},[82],{"type":45,"value":83},"2.2. Digital Products: The digital nature of our deliverables means they cannot be \"returned\" once accessed or delivered.",{"type":40,"tag":47,"props":85,"children":86},{},[87],{"type":45,"value":88},"2.3. Time-Based Services: Many of our services are time-based, and the time spent cannot be reclaimed once used.",{"type":40,"tag":52,"props":90,"children":92},{"id":91},"_3-quality-assurance",[93],{"type":45,"value":94},"3. Quality Assurance",{"type":40,"tag":47,"props":96,"children":97},{},[98],{"type":45,"value":99},"While we do not offer refunds, we are committed to delivering high-quality services:",{"type":40,"tag":47,"props":101,"children":102},{},[103],{"type":45,"value":104},"3.1. We work closely with our clients throughout the project to ensure satisfaction at each stage.",{"type":40,"tag":47,"props":106,"children":107},{},[108],{"type":45,"value":109},"3.2. Our team is dedicated to meeting the agreed-upon specifications and deliverables outlined in our service contract.",{"type":40,"tag":47,"props":111,"children":112},{},[113],{"type":45,"value":114},"3.3. In the unlikely event that we fail to deliver the agreed-upon services, we will work diligently to rectify the situation at no additional cost.",{"type":40,"tag":52,"props":116,"children":118},{"id":117},"_4-exceptions",[119],{"type":45,"value":120},"4. Exceptions",{"type":40,"tag":47,"props":122,"children":123},{},[124],{"type":45,"value":125},"4.1. In extraordinary circumstances, AGIQuantron Technologies reserves the right to consider refunds on a case-by-case basis. However, the issuance of a refund is at the sole discretion of AGIQuantron Technologies and is not guaranteed.",{"type":40,"tag":47,"props":127,"children":128},{},[129],{"type":45,"value":130},"4.2. Any exceptions to this policy must be agreed upon in writing before the commencement of services.",{"type":40,"tag":52,"props":132,"children":134},{"id":133},"_5-cancellation-of-services",[135],{"type":45,"value":136},"5. Cancellation of Services",{"type":40,"tag":47,"props":138,"children":139},{},[140],{"type":45,"value":141},"5.1. If you wish to cancel a service before work has commenced, please contact us immediately. Cancellation terms will be as specified in our service agreement.",{"type":40,"tag":47,"props":143,"children":144},{},[145],{"type":45,"value":146},"5.2. For ongoing services, cancellation notices and procedures will be as outlined in our service contract.",{"type":40,"tag":52,"props":148,"children":150},{"id":149},"_6-dispute-resolution",[151],{"type":45,"value":152},"6. Dispute Resolution",{"type":40,"tag":47,"props":154,"children":155},{},[156],{"type":45,"value":157},"In the event of a dispute regarding our services, we are committed to working with our clients to reach a mutually satisfactory resolution. If a resolution cannot be reached, the dispute will be handled as per the terms outlined in our service agreement.",{"type":40,"tag":52,"props":159,"children":161},{"id":160},"_7-changes-to-this-policy",[162],{"type":45,"value":163},"7. Changes to This Policy",{"type":40,"tag":47,"props":165,"children":166},{},[167],{"type":45,"value":168},"We reserve the right to modify this refund poli